        .om
            section
                h1 le modèle

            aside <a href="https://5ht.co">Maxim Sokhatsky</a>
                time 20 DEC 2018
            p.
                Here is the conceptual model of a theorem-proving system
                that unifies tower of type systems with runtime components
                (as extraction targets). The model has presented here as
                a set of 1) calculi with its models; 2) programs and base
                libraries; and 3) program transformations: type checking,
                compilation, type erasure, code extraction, optimization, etc.
            p.
                While being a generic blueprint, some parts of the model
                implemented in various languages. The research was founded
                by Synrc Research Center, Kyiv, Ukraine. All works were
                done under the supervision of Pavlo Maslianko, National
                Technical University of Ukraine «Igor Sikorsky Kyiv
                Polytechnic Institute» Faculty of Applied Mathematics.

            section
                h1 TAXONOMIE
            p.
                The thesis is grouped by research areas with their corresponding
                type systems, formal models, type checkers and base libraries.

